{"tid":194420,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大陸客遊冰島毀景觀　取石頭砌「中國」捱轟","createTime":"2017-04-10T03:03:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-10T03:55:48.000Z","uid":30561,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"49fc9b47ed2e3d29018918604f3fe258fb528c9e","tid":194420,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T03:03:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170409/photo/bkncn-20170409061624948-0409_05011_001_01p.jpg?20170409162418\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170409%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20170409061624948-0409_05011_001_01p.jpg%3F20170409162418&h=3fa884a8&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n冰島西部的斯奈山半島（Sn&aelig;fellsnes），其自然景觀有「攝影師天堂」的美譽。惟近日竟揭發有疑似中國遊客，用島上石頭排出圖案及簡體中文「中國」大字，破壞自然景觀，惹來冰島居民和其他多國遊客強烈不滿。 <br />\n<br />\n有冰島媒體以「故意破壞斯奈山半島，為了拍出中國」為題（Skemmdarverk &aacute; Sn&aelig;fellsnesi: &bdquo;Sendu myndina &aacute; k&iacute;nversk yfirv&ouml;ld&ldquo;）報道此事，更特別標明，「符號（即簡體中文字）的意思是中國，遊客不負責任行為，又一實例」。從圖片所見，有人在地上用石頭，排出一個同心圓圖案和簡體中文的「中國」兩個字。 <br />\n<br />\n據了解，斯奈山半島實際一直備受當地人及到訪遊客愛護，今次事件前並無人做同類行為，涉事中國遊客可說是「開創先河」，有當地居民亦坦言擔心類似事件會陸續發生。 <br />\n<br />\n報道又引述一名比利時遊客表示，對做出上述行為的中國遊客感到十分憤怒；亦有另一名德國遊客認為，應該要進一步將紀錄惡行的照片寄送予中國政府，交給他們調查，找到涉事者後將其列入黑名單；有其他中國網民得知報道後留言，為這些「同胞」感到丟臉。"},{"pid":"99c0827cd8b5de99969e57d69e523a79c4975059","tid":194420,"uid":47797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T03:04:39.000Z","msg":"祖國萬歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fc7a9e929202a53ac9c885bdbf00cca8e69d474","tid":194420,"uid":5077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T03:14:31.000Z","msg":"調查調到撚咩"},{"pid":"a7cedee1af4f42c3100c6f17bc8d277d8e2bd9c6","tid":194420,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T03:16:00.000Z","msg":"北歐五國應該禁止鄰國遊客入境啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"febac51927bef9914debc9161e3f5e160732b59d","tid":194420,"uid":73942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T03:17:36.000Z","msg":"查下十幾億人入面有幾多個唔會做呢d行為好撚過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4efa32c66d544dbce98f28ece9ed490641810362","tid":194420,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T03:17:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>北歐五國應該禁止鄰國遊客入境啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你仆硬街 佢地會向特衰護照埋手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港人隨時被black list"},{"pid":"40dd867c5cbfcdc8976ccaa48725b702deb7d675","tid":194420,"uid":35581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T03:23:01.000Z","msg":"堆網民出到去咪又會咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n淨係識笑人 但其實佢地都一樣"},{"pid":"53e170ff807491997a407b7e26f3c1d58f627bb1","tid":194420,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T03:25:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d0119ab37018722057e6696ad404760a2248ae6","tid":194420,"uid":57376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T03:28:28.000Z","msg":"做完柒事仲要話俾全世界人知，支那人智商真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/nor